                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>\n                <date>July 11th 5614</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Rev Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am sorry I could not<lb/> keep my promise to send you the rev<lb/>\n                of the manuscript from <placeName>New York</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The fact is I felt so warm and<lb/> fatigued there that I could not\n                attend to<lb/> any thing and was actually glad to get<lb/> home as soon as\n                possible.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Enclosed you will find the<lb/>\n                <sic>ballance</sic> of the article. I am not aware<lb/> whether or not I lost some\n                of the intermed<lb/>iate pages, you will be able to see <sic>wether</sic> the\n                connection is there or not, should a few<lb/> lines be wanting I trust to your\n                good<lb/> taste and <sic>judgement</sic> to supply the<lb/> deficiency.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Trusting that you are<lb/> in the enjoyment of good health, a\n                bless-<lb/>ing which I and mine thank God enjoy</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">My dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">yours most respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Solomon Jacobs</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3vt1h933/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
